{"tid":1703851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【以正視聽】Roadblock教室，前線唔該入嚟睇睇","createTime":"2019-11-10T12:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T13:10:00.000Z","uid":235161,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1c98fc3281a819089fc80ce4b066ad66ff4739b3","tid":1703851,"uid":235161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:47:09.000Z","msg":"Set Roadblock 係每次快閃同示威嘅基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的係為咗<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">阻街</span></span></strong>，<strong>[size=4<span style=\"color: gold;\">]唔畀車行</span>[/size=4]</strong>，可以幫人罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但最主要唔係畀狗車接近手足</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但小弟發現咗樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家Set完Roadblock係會放車走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁Set嚟有咩用呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明知呢度會有示威都嚟呢條路，一係佢on9，一係佢係嚟用自己架車嚟整大型Roadblock<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前有個post發現咗水炮車嘅春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係塞車!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔該各位手足Set完Roadblock唔好再畀車過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n否則係害咗手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者Set之前畀警告(舉旗)，希望大家集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11月11，黎明之戰</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4d102e2e01b1d54319f54f57c80b807af4e89d","tid":1703851,"uid":235161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"每次見到手足放完一架又架就好心up"},{"pid":"5057140d6b066c53a2428b3595cb86ac2758eeae","tid":1703851,"uid":235161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:49:03.000Z","msg":"大大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95df02c9f0b5c9c6c3e9cb0ae5d62fa3b77ea721","tid":1703851,"uid":235161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"大大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9f0e65d86f1e7da4fa93055fe701b9469f0d5f","tid":1703851,"uid":235161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:49:56.000Z","msg":"大大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087c8ebcef5739bb40024968f9188ef89015fc72","tid":1703851,"uid":315227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手，聽日落街之後<br />\n嗌兩下口號，叫醒埋其他手足"},{"pid":"84e1e1f10934d27ea725a452aaad00e51be4beb8","tid":1703851,"uid":235161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"大大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /